                </div>

                <div class="copywrap" id="copyBlock">â€¦</div>
                <div class="footer">Â© Cyberâ€‘TeK(IT) â€¢ HTA template with blue header and Close button</div>
            </div>

            <details class="card">
                <summary>Details & Notes</summary>
                <div style="margin-top:10px; font-size:12px; color:#c1cbe2;">
                    â€¢ OS values are sourced from WMI (Win32_OperatingSystem).<br/>
                    â€¢ Privilege status checks local Administrators group membership and falls back to a command check if needed.<br/>
                    â€¢ Use the <b>Refresh</b> button after privilege or account changes.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
